item.description: The Tea House is charming, serving formal full tea and a la carte, breakfast, sandwiches, etc the food is delish.
item.why: The first meetup I went to with this fantastic group was at the Wenham Tea House, about a year ago, and I'd love to celebrate the first day of Spring - and my birthday - here with you lovely ladies!
